	These beautifully fragranced bath salts are deeply hydrating and skin softening. They contain real rose petals and the finest essential oils. They have a woody floral fragrance, opening with lemon and orange, followed by a bouquet of jasmine, gardenia, rose and lavender on a base of patchouli, sandalwood and musk. This fantastic concoction of oils enables you to relax and drift away with the lovely aromas. These bath salts come in a beautifully decorated plastic tub making them a wonderful gift idea, or a perfect treat for yourself. Directions for use: sprinkle roughly a heaped tablespoon of bath salts under warm running water and ensure they mix in well using your hand.&nbsp;These bath salts are suitable for vegans.&nbsp;</p>
